---

---

<section
  class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-y border-white/[0.06] px-6 py-32 sm:py-40 lg:py-48"
>
  <!-- Subtle grid -->
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 grid-bg opacity-50"
  ></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <p
      data-reveal
      class="text-center text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent-500"
    >
      Manifeste
    </p>

    <h2
      data-reveal
      data-split-text
      class="display-manifesto mt-8 text-balance text-center text-ink-50"
    >
      Vos données. Vos règles. Votre asso.
    </h2>

    <p
      data-reveal
      class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-400 sm:text-lg"
    >
      Konclav est un outil. Pas un produit qui transforme vos membres en
      données vendables. Pas de pub. Pas d'analytics tierces. Pas de
      « data partner ». Vous payez l'app, vous possédez tout.
    </p>

    <div
      data-reveal
      class="mx-auto mt-12 flex max-w-lg flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 text-[11px] text-ink-500"
    >
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="h-3 w-3 text-accent-500" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M13.5 4.5 6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        Aucun tracker
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="h-3 w-3 text-accent-500" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M13.5 4.5 6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        Hébergé en UE
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="h-3 w-3 text-accent-500" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M13.5 4.5 6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        Export à tout moment
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="h-3 w-3 text-accent-500" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M13.5 4.5 6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        Sans engagement
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
